{"type":"text","timestamp":1775866908552,"sessionID":"ses_286197a78ffew2etUbcd1oyk8z","part":{"id":"prt_d79ea6e9b001BBkjk4M1eyAwu8","messageID":"msg_d79ea61cd001A1m4i4j4uY33Cb","sessionID":"ses_286197a78ffew2etUbcd1oyk8z","type":"text","text":"The delta-spec.md file for AR-013 has been successfully written. Here's a summary of what was created:\n\n**File:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-013/delta-spec.md` (586 lines)\n\nThe specification includes comprehensive GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios for:\n\n### Redis Store Implementation (30+ scenarios)\n- Ping connectivity verification\n- GetSandboxBySessionID with ErrNotFound handling\n- StoreSandbox validation (nil, empty SessionID, zero ExpiresAt)\n- StoreSandbox atomic pipeline execution\n- UpdateSandbox with XX flag semantics\n- DeleteSandboxBySessionID cleanup\n- ListExpiredSandboxes / ListInactiveSandboxes with ZRANGEBYSCORE\n- UpdateSessionLastActivity with existence verification\n- Close connection handling\n\n### Valkey Store Implementation (30+ scenarios)\n- Same coverage as Redis but using Valkey-specific API patterns\n- DoMulti for atomic operations\n- IsValkeyNil error handling\n- MGET for batch loading\n\n### Environment Configuration (10+ scenarios)\n- REDIS_ADDR and REDIS_PASSWORD validation\n- REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED case-insensitive handling\n- VALKEY_ADDR parsing (comma-separated)\n- VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE and VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE options\n\n### Additional sections\n- Changes to Base Specification\n- New Interfaces (internal types)\n- Behavioral Changes table\n- Dependencies\n- File Index\n- Constants\n- Environment Variables table\n- Migration Notes\n- Acceptance Criteria Summary\n\nNote: The LSP errors shown are pre-existing issues in the implementation files (`redis.go`, `valkey.go`), not related to the delta-spec.md document that was created.","time":{"start":1775866908550,"end":1775866908550}}}
